Mikely Wilhelm Adam (amụrụ na Jenụwarị 8, 1992), nke a maara nke ọma site na aha egwu ya bụ Mike Free, bụ onye America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ, DJ, na ónyé na-ede egwu si South Central, Los Angeles. Mgbè ọ na-aga Mahadum Hampton na Virginia, Free malitere iso DJ Mustard rụọ ọrụ, ónyé mèrè ka ọ mata ndị na-ese ihe na Los Angeles gụnyere YG na Ty Dolla Sign. Ihe ịga nke ọma mbụ nke Free bịara site na ọrụ mmepụta ya na Tygaʹs "Rack City" na DJ Mustard, nke ụlọ ọrụ Recording Industry Association of America (RIAA) kwadoro ugboro anọ platinum.
